      "content": "Interesting. You mentioned that the \"uncertainty and volatility of the local community\" in Profile B is a risk factor. Can you elaborate on why demographic shifts and high churn specifically lead to downward pressure on property values? Is there a specific correlation between a lack of demographic homogeneity and economic instability in these types of urban environments?",
